# return wine aging level
def get_wine_aging(year_diff):
    if year_diff > 1091:
        return 'collection'
    elif year_diff > 545:
        return 'vintage'
    elif year_diff > 363:
        return 'aged'
    else:
        return 'young'

MinMaxScaler [0,1], , 0 1 .

:

  • : $$ x-min $$
  • : $$ max-min $$
$$ x_{scaled} = \frac{x-x_{min}}{x_{max}-x_{min}} $$

, 10 35 . 17 .

:

$$ x_{scaled} = \frac{(17-10)}{(35-10)} = 0,28 $$
